    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a mechanically sound example of the high-revving S65 4.0L V8 era. The naturally aspirated powerplant pulls cleanly to its 8,400 RPM redline, paired with a tactile 6-speed manual gearbox and a Variable M Differential Lock for optimal longitudinal and lateral dynamics. To ensure long-term reliability, the rod bearings and throttle actuators have been proactively serviced. The chassis features Electronic Damping Control (EDC), providing adjustable damping rates that complement the communicative hydraulic steering rack. While the exterior and interior show honest patina consistent with a well-driven enthusiast car, the drivetrain remains robust with no VANOS issues or fluid leaks. This is a driver-spec machine optimized for performance and mechanical longevity.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
