    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between performance and daily practicality. The exterior retains a deep luster and a smooth finish, though a keen eye might spot a few minor stone chips on the front fascia consistent with careful highway use. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the premium upholstery has been regularly conditioned and shows only slight softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster, with no tears or unpleasant odors. Every feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system, functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is robust. I have adhered to a strict maintenance schedule, with the most recent service including a full synthetic oil change, a new air filter, and a comprehensive brake inspection. The tires offer significant remaining tread, ensuring a smooth and confident ride for the next owner. Included with the sale are all original manuals and a detailed folder of service receipts to verify its history. This is a dependable, well-cared-for example ready for its next chapter.",
      "price": 36500.0,
